text: Randall Shedd (born March 5, 1953) is an American politician. He is a member of the Alabama House of Representatives from the 11th District, serving since 2013. He is a member of the Republican Party. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Members of the Alabama House of Representatives Category:Alabama Republicans Category:People from Arab, Alabama Category:21st- century American politicians Category:1953 births
